Class Filter

  Filter(string name, string logFilePath)
    The name will also be the name of the .regex file

  Run()
    The entry point for the filter's main thread

  Register(Action act)
    Add an Action object to call on when a filter matches


Class Action

  Action(string name)
    name will be the name of the .act file that contains the shell commands

  Act(string host, int banSeconds)
    Act will read in this objects .act file line by line, replace and key in the
    provided map in the command with the corresponding value, then execute it
    with a call to system()
